trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier" /> class identifies an HTTP server.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier" /> identifica um servidor HTTP.

trans-unit.source: This class is used to identify a server that provides DSML over SOAP/HTTP.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é usada para identificar um servidor que fornece DSML por SOAP/HTTP.

trans-unit.source: A server represented as a <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Um servidor representado como um objeto <see cref="T:System.Uri" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier.#ctor(System.Uri)" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier" /> class using the specified parameter.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier.#ctor(System.Uri)" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier" /> usando o parâmetro especificado.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="serverUri" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="serverUri" /> é uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="serverUri" /> scheme is not http or https.
trans-unit.target: O esquema <paramref name="serverUri" /> não é http ou https.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier.ServerUri" /> property contains the <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> of the server this object identifies.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier.ServerUri" /> contém o <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> do servidor que esse objeto identifica.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> of the server this object identifies.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> do servidor identifica esse objeto.
